	<hgroup>
		<h1>About</h1>
		<h2>Chris Basham is a <abbr title="User Experience">UX</abbr> designer and web developer pursuing a masters in <a href="http://hcid.informatics.indiana.edu"><abbr title="Human-Computer Interaction Design">HCI/d</abbr></a> at <a href="http://www.iub.edu">Indiana University Bloomington</a>. He is currently seeking an <abbr title="User Experience">UX</abbr> internship for summer 2010.</h2>
